[10:05] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'it saves a lot of tokens. &gt;&gt; [music] &gt;&gt; Another big advantage of Space Agent is the customizability and extensibility. &gt;&gt; [music] &gt;&gt; The agent lives in a virtual file system that is accessible by the front end.'

[10:18] [scene:talk]
